---
---
<section class="hero container">
  <div class="hero-badge glass">✨ Nueva colección 2026</div>
  <h1>Tecnología que se siente <span class="grad-text">del futuro</span></h1>
  <p>Descubre gadgets premium con envío gratis, garantía extendida y devoluciones sin preguntas durante 30 días.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="#productos" class="btn-primary">Explorar productos</a>
    <a href="#productos" class="btn-ghost glass">Ver ofertas 🔥</a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div><strong>+12K</strong><span>Clientes felices</span></div>
    <div><strong>4.8★</strong><span>Valoración media</span></div>
    <div><strong>24h</strong><span>Envío express</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero { text-align: center; padding-top: 90px; padding-bottom: 70px; }
  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-dim); margin-bottom: 26px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.2rem);
    font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.08; letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }
  p {
    color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 34px;
  }
  .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn-primary {
    padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 999px; text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--grad-cta); background-size: 200% 200%;
    color: #fff; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4);
    transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    animation: shimmer 5s ease infinite;
  }
  @keyframes shimmer {
    0%, 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.55); }
  .btn-ghost {
    padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 999px; text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.15s, background 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); background: var(--surface-2); }
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex; gap: 56px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 60px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .hero-stats div { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .hero-stats strong { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .hero-stats span { color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 0.88rem; }
</style>
